---
title: Honey Mustard Pork with Roasted Pumpkin & Cucumber Salad
description: This classic honey mustard combo brings so much flavour to juicy pork steaks. Serve them with sweet roasted veggies and a crisp
cucumber salad for a winning nutritious dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
